latestPosts.caption:
#gifted Hosting this Easter, but not looking forward to lots of baking? I've got you covered with LE CHIC PATISSIER. 

On the bottom tier, we are plating the Chocolate Chip Brioche Bread, which is literally the softest bread that I have ever had, and also comes in a  butter flavor. The second tier, are thier Original Gluten-free Macarons, and come in flavors, Chocolate, Raspberry, Vanilla, Salted Caramel, Lemon, and Pistachio. They also have pink, heart-shaped ones as well. And the final tier is their lovely Liège Belgian Waffles, and comes individually wrapped for quick grab and go snacks. Mitchell and I almost ate them all right after i was done filming.  Lol The next time you need quick hosting snacks or just a few small little bits, look to LE CHIC PATISSIER. 🍞🧇💖💛💚
